msgid "Remove the built-in media controls from the system date/time menu"
msgstr "Supprimer les contrôles multimédia intégrés du menu date/heure"

#: prefs.js:260
msgid ""
"When ON, the extension hides the stock GNOME media controls that\n"
"normally appear in the calendar / notification panel (the date-time\n"
"menu). This prevents a duplicate 'now playing' widget.\n"
"\n"
"The built-in controls are fully restored the moment you:\n"
"  • Turn this switch off, or\n"
"  • Disable or uninstall this extension."
