#: prefs.js:1161
msgid "Double-click the album art"
msgstr "Double-cliquer sur la pochette"

#: prefs.js:1163
msgid ""
"Double-click the album art image in the popup to toggle the vinyl record "
"style for that specific app or browser source. For browsers (Chrome, "
"Firefox, etc.) each site (YouTube, YouTube Music, Spotify Web) is stored as "
"its own separate entry."
